<bibRefCitation author="Robertson, D. R. &amp; Allen, G. R." box="[527,809,762,789]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" refId="ref66239" refString="Robertson, D. R. &amp; Allen, G. R. (2015) Shorefishes of the Tropical Eastern Pacific: online information system. Version 2.0. Smithsonian Tropical Research Institute, Balboa, Panama. Available from: https: // biogeodb. stri. si. edu / sftep / en / pages (accessed 27 August 2021)." type="url" year="2015">Robertson &amp; Allen 2015</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
